{
  "chapter": 15,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙被雅夫人设计带入府中，赵穆策划用春药\"贞女荡\"暗害他，使其在比武中输给连晋。项少龙因受过抗体训练昏迷后迅速苏醒，识破阴谋，将计就计反将春药喂给雅夫人和翠娘，使二人虚凰假凤。次日他装作体力不支，瞒过乌应元和陶方，后向二人坦白真相。赵宫祥瑞大殿举行晚宴，赵穆当众逼连晋表态投靠，连晋被迫应允。项少龙从容入场，众人见他面色灰白皆以为他必败，实则他已将计就计，准备反戈一击。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙不要怪我，我是被逼的，不这样做，我们会很惨的。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "侯爷！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "侯爷要干什么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "没什么！试试他的反应罢了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "还不信奴家吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "小心驶得万年船，我哪知你不是和他合起来骗我。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "骚娘儿愈来愈丰满哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "你今天还糟塌得人家不够吗？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "又想了吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "假如我娶了你，赵雅你肯否放弃这小子而跟随我呢？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "侯爷不要作弄奴家了，你看上的只是乌廷芳，怎会是我这人尽可夫的残花败柳呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "这么有弹性，怎会是残花败柳，好了！我不逼你，只要你依我之言办事，这小子明晚后就是你的了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "我真不明白，项少龙就算输了，乌氏倮亦绝不肯把他的宝贝孙女送你，你这样对付项少龙有什么作用？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "本人自有妙计，这个不用你去管。嘿！告诉我，我和这小子谁摸得你更舒服？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "当然是侯爷逗得人家厉害。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "那为何我拿这小子来和你交易，你便立即投降？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "侯爷抓痛人家了。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "先答我！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "因为你对我只有欲，而他对我除肉欲外，还有爱。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "弄醒他后，翠娘会给他喂一粒'贞女荡'，你自己若受不了，教翠娘代你，千万不可勉强，事后让他沉睡三个时辰，才好把他唤醒。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "真的没事吗？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "看你关心他的样子，我真想把这小子杀掉。放心吧！他除了因春药而致消耗大量体力外，一切均与常人无异，只不过那场比武他注定会败给连晋。记着，明晚你要陪连晋，以后的事我再不管你。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_niang",
      "speaker_name": "翠娘",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "夫人见谅，侯爷吩咐小婢定要目睹整个过程，他很给夫人面子的了！否则他最爱看的就是这类事，若来的不是小婢而是他，夫人就更难堪了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_niang",
      "speaker_name": "翠娘",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "成了！这药入口即溶，流进咽喉，什么贞烈和意志坚强的人都禁受不起。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_niang",
      "speaker_name": "翠娘",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "让小婢取水来弄醒他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_cui_niang",
      "text": "假若他醒来知我喂他春药，事后岂非恨死人家？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_niang",
      "speaker_name": "翠娘",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "放心吧！他受药力所制，神智会陷在半昏迷状态，只知戮力以赴，夫人好好享受！我看他壮健如牛，夫人待会儿说不定还要求我替上哩！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_bi",
      "speaker_name": "俏婢",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "乌家的大少爷在正厅等候项爷，项爷你没什么吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qiao_bi",
      "text": "水！给我一点水！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_bi",
      "speaker_name": "俏婢",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项爷昨晚过劳哩！夫人也像你那样子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "情况有点不妙，我看少龙是着了雅夫人的道儿，陶公快去请黄妙手来，看看可否在比武前恢复他的精神体力。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "若要我由现在起一直装作昏迷，会比打我一顿更难过。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙真了得，那针上的毒药定是由昏麻草提炼出来的汁液，刺入血脉里，马儿都要昏迷，想不到对你竟不起作用。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这可说是天运仍在我们这一方，少龙准备怎样运用此优势？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "我会教赵穆和连晋大吃一惊。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "刚才雅夫人使人来问你的情况，我把那人赶走，假设她亲来见你，少龙要不要见她。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "还是不见为妙。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "这春药虽厉害，不过听赵穆的语气，睡上几个时辰后，体力应可恢复少许，只不过绝应付不了激烈的打斗。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这才是道理，否则连晋胜之不武，如何在大王和众公卿大臣前立威。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "我同意大少爷的话，不见任何人，使敌人以为我正致力恢复体力，今晚可不用扮得那么辛苦。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不过少龙至少要装作力竭筋疲的样子，起行前我为你脸上敷点灰粉，那就更万无一失了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你为何要害少龙，假设他有何不测，我定不放过你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_zong",
      "speaker_name": "郭纵",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "text": "听说项少龙昨晚还到雅夫人处鬼混，如此不知自爱，如何可成大事，看来他今晚必败无疑。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "廷芳小姐，久违了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "侯爷你好！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": "char_guo_zong",
      "text": "你郭家手下能人众多，不如找个人出来让我们开开眼界。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "text": "乌老板若同意，本侯想请连晋坐到我那一席去。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "若连晋欢喜，老夫怎会不同意。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "连晋",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "多谢侯爷赏识，连某怎敢不从命。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": "char_lian_jin",
      "text": "连晋你今晚定要尽力为侯爷争光，只许胜不许败！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙过来！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    }
  ],
